	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Egi tibi gratias pro tua temporum digestione<note xml:id="fna" type="footnote" n="a">Zu dieser Schrift s. auch <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p7844">Wolrads</persName> Tagebuch vom <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l18" cert="high">Augsburger</placeName> RT 1548, ed. Tross, S. 37f.</note> adiunxique illis literis meis, quę tum videbantur necessaria; misi autem meas per quendam literatum, qui se <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p20817" cert="high">Clementem</persName> appellabat<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">Ev. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p20817" cert="high">Clemens Lenner</persName>? Vgl. <bibl><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8049" cert="high">Vadian</persName> BW</bibl> VI, Reg., und unten Nr. 18125. - Laut e-Mail von Rainer Henrich vom 15.04.2014 handelt es sich eher um den St. Galler "Lesmaister" und Musiker Clemens Hör.</note>; spero eas tibi esse redditas.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nunc scias nobis per <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18538" cert="high">Cesaream maiestatem</persName> esse formulam religionis, quę vocatur Interim, pręscriptam et publicatam, iuxta quam et credi et agi vult <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18538" cert="high">Cęsar</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Principio de peccato et iustificatione non admodum male disponitur, nisi quod opera nimium licenter adiungantur.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sacramentorum numerus est 7, de quibus omnibus perperam docetur, presertim de cena domini et missa, in qua transsubstantiationem panis et vini, venerationem et intercessionem demortuorum sanctorum et oblationem corporis et sanguinis Christi per sacerdotem aperte inducunt.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Item coniugium sacerdotale et communionem sub utraque spetie, quantum ad laycos pertinet, tantum usque ad definitionem vel determinationem <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1107" cert="high">Tridentini</placeName> concilii tolerant.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Pręterea nemo concionari debet nisi ordinatus et approbatus ab episcopis ordinatiis.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Summa: preter papatum nihil aliud est et in hoc peior, quod papistę laudantur propter constantiam et perseverationem in pristina eorum religione, admonentur quoque, ut ita perdurent, reliqui vero, ut ad ecclesiam eorum revertamtur, multum incitantur.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">In quo papatus per comnia confirmatur, cęteri vero omnes dmnantur.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hoc iugum super et pręterterrena omnia conculcata ferimus, atque hęc est sors nostra, quoniam sine cruce christianus non emergit.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ora diligenter pro nobis, atque si contigerit me in his erumnis oppetere, te visurus sum in aeterna patria.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Salveant tui omnes, <persName ref="p8018" cert="high">Hallerus</persName>, <persName ref="p8011" cert="high">Gvaltherus</persName>.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Afflictio vestra haud ita longe abest.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dux <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18250" cert="high">Mauritius Saxo</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p20434" cert="high">Ioannes marchio Brandenburgensis</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18935">dux Zweyprucken</persName> et Civitates nolunt in hoc Interim consentire.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quod si violentia accesserit, certe <persName type="auto_name">Neroniana</persName> vel <persName type="auto_name">Maximiana</persName> clades sequetur.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="de" type="auto">20. maii.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="signature">[Unterschrift fehlt.]</note>
					<note type="address">[Adresse:]</note>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Herren <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Heinrichen Bullinger</persName> zu <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l587" cert="high">Zurch</placeName> etc. zu handen.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l587" cert="high">Zurch</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
